{
    "title": "Quase Um Segundo",
    "artist": "Herbert Vianna",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro 4x] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab\">Ab</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu queria ver no escuro do mundo</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aonde está tudo o que você quer</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra me transformar no que te agrada</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No que me faça ver</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quais são as cores e as coisas pra te prender</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7/D\">Bb7/D</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu tive um sonho ruim e acordei chorando</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por isso eu te liguei</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa em mim</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm7(9)\">Fm7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7(13)\">Bb7(13)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb6\">Eb6</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/D\">Bb/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lá lá lá lá lá lá lá</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ás vezes te odeio por quase um segundo</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/D\">Bb/D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Depois te amo mais</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Teus pêlos, teu rosto, teu gosto, tudo</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo que não me deixa em paz</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quais são as cores e as coisas pra te prender</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7/D\">Bb7/D</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu tive um sonho ruim e acordei chorando</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por isso eu te liguei</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa em mim</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm7(9)\">Fm7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7(13)\">Bb7(13)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb6\">Eb6</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/D\">Bb/D</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lá lá lá lá lá lá lá</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ás vezes te odeio por quase um segundo</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Depois te amo mais</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Teus pêlos, teu rosto, teu gosto, tudo</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo que não me deixa em paz</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quais são as cores e as coisas pra te prender</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7/D\">Bb7/D</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu tive um sonho ruim e acordei chorando</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por isso eu te liguei</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb/F\">Bb/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa em mim</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7M(9)\">Eb7M(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/E\">D/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Será que você ainda pensa</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm7(9)\">Fm7(9)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7(13)\">Bb7(13)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/E\">C/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lá lá lá lá lá lá lá</span>\n",
